<br />

<br />
Bring the healing abilities of mages uo to par with beastlords (possibly increasing for both classes.  I think a 500 mana 5k heal, 9 sec cast time would be great).  
<br />

<br />
Increase the aggro for certain mage pet types.
<br />

<br />
Make an AA where you can place pet on a certain mob and ensure that it stays locked on that target and not others.
<br />

<br />
Allow pets to inherit the runspeed of it's owner.
<br />

<br />
Take away the mana component and get rid of some of the spells from 60+ fire pet (root is about worthless).
<br />

<br />
Make mage pet spells procs instead of spells (similar to bsts, so no attack rounds are lost).
<br />

<br />
Increase base 65 earth pet hps at about 7k (it should be a tank, afterall).
<br />

<br />
Increase pet damage output (see no reason why a 60_ water pet couldn't land a backstab (non-crit) for 500 damage.  This does not encroach on rogues in one bit.
<br />

<br />
Give WoX a built in 25 pct haste (stackable with burnout and mask (increase haste cap if need be)).  I have always envisioned a creature of air to be fast hell.<br />_________________<br />Churizo Andeggs
